<article class="sidebar-split">
    <div class="mainbar">
        <p>Welcome to Workout.Planner!</p>
        <p>
            Are you interested in going to the gym, but frustrated at making a workout routine every time
            you go? Planning a full workout routine for the week can be time consuming and difficult to always remember.

        </p>
        <p>
            So instead with the help of <strong>Workout.Planner</strong> you can manage your routines by the day and never forget what your goals
            are.

        </p>

        <h2>Why a bookshelf?</h2>
        <p>a
            I used to love visiting friends and seeing what was on their
            bookshelves. Scanning the books and magazines and old newspaper
            clippings on a bookshelf is such a unique way of understanding how
            someone thinks, and what's on their mind.
        </p>
        <p>
            These days we're all curators online. We send and share links
            and recommendations <em>all the time</em>. But we rarely get to look at
            others' shelves in the same way. <strong>Shelf.page</strong> is an
            attempt to revive that feeling, on the Internet.
        </p>
        <a href="/about">about</a>
    </div>
